title: Seraphon Saurus Warrior Alpha in 8 paints
description:
Saurus Warriors are the brutal, roaring heart of the Seraphon armies - feared for unleashing their cold-blooded savagery in the midst of battle. In this video, we’ll be painting a Saurus Warrior Alpha in just 8 paints so you can get the unit ready to join their kin in battle in no time.
        
If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it
